HEADWORD: irredenta
<hw>irredenta</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A region that is related
ethnically or historically to one country but is controlled politically
by another.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> irridenta.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>irredentism</ent>⟦br⟧
